{
  "_comment": "Pi-compatible custom provider config. Source of truth (human-readable, with weights/context_modes): ~/Code/claude-code-config/models.yaml. All Pi traffic routes through LiteLLM proxy on :4000 — never direct to Ollama. The `reasoning` flag below marks models that emit a <think> channel; set Pi's thinking level accordingly when calling these.",
